monio artesanal de Puerto Rico.</div></div><hr><p><strong>¿Te quedaste con ganas de más?</strong>&nbsp;Síguenos en&nbsp;<strong>Instagram</strong>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://instagram.com/obrasdelpais?utm_medium=copy_link&ref=obrasdelpais.com\">obrasdelpais</a>) y&nbsp;<strong>Facebook</strong>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/obrasdelpais/\">Obras del País</a>) para contenido adicional de cada artesano.&nbsp;<strong>Y si te gustó el corto documental, coméntalo y compártelo.</strong>&nbsp;Queremos saber qué opinan. 🤗✨</p><h2 id=\"-1\"></h2>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div>\n</div>\t\t<div class=\"post-meta\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"post-share\">\r\n\t<a class=\"twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Deborah%20Feliciano%2C%20fachadas%20del%20Viejo%20San%20Juan%20sobre%20bamb%C3%BA&amp;url=https://www.obrasdelpais.com/nuevo-microdoc-deborah-feliciano-fachadas-sobre-bambu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><svg class=\"global-svg\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M23.954 4.569c-.885.389-1.83.654-2.825.775 1.014-.611 1.794-1.574 2.163-2.723-.951.555-2.005.959-3.127 1.184-.896-.959-2.173-1.559-3.591-1.559-2.717 0-4.92 2.203-4.92 4.917 0 .39.045.765.127 1.124C7.691 8.094 4.066 6.13 1.64 3.161c-.427.722-.666 1.561-.666 2.475 0 1.71.87 3.213 2.188 4.096-.807-.026-1.566-.248-2.228-.616v.061c0 2.385 1.693 4.374 3.946 4.827-.413.111-.849.171-1.296.171-.314 0-.615-.03-.916-.086.631 1.953 2.445 3.377 4.604 3.417-1.68 1.319-3.809 2.105-6.102 2.105-.39 0-.779-.023-1.17-.067 2.189 1.394 4.768 2.209 7.557 2.209 9.054 0 13.999-7.496 13.999-13.986 0-.209 0-.42-.015-.63.961-.689 1.8-1.56 2.46-2.548l-.047-.02z\"/></svg></a>\r\n\t<a class=\"facebook\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.obrasdelpais.com/nuevo-microdoc-deborah-feliciano-fachadas-sobre-bambu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><svg class=\"global-svg\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"